definition: to weave/to plait/to organize/to group/to arrange/to edit/to compile/to write/to compose/to fabricate
to form/to organize/group/team/classifier for sets, series, groups of people, batteries

sentences.english: Categorizing is another means of organization.
sentences.chinese: 分类编组是另一种方法。

sentences.english: Now you need a class to handle marshalling.
sentences.chinese: 现在需要一个类处理编组。

sentences.english: The common base is that implementations must be able to unmarshal valid documents.
sentences.chinese: 根据常理，实现必须能够反编组有效的文档。

sentences.english: The author applies fuzzy comprehensive evaluation method to evaluate the comprehensive automation of Huaihua South Marshalling Station.
sentences.chinese: 应用模糊综合评价法对怀化南编组站自动化进行评价。

sentences.english: The air traffic service (ATS) telegraphs are composed of fixed information groups.
sentences.chinese: 空中交通服务电报采用固定的信息编组方式组织报文。

sentences.english: A hump glide video system applied to the railway marshalling station was devised.
sentences.chinese: 设计了一个用于铁路编组站的驼峰溜放视频系统。

sentences.english: I'll also examine any changes that take place from when a document is originally unmarshalled to when it is marshalled back into an output format.
sentences.chinese: 我还将考察文档在解组和编组过程中发生的任何变化。

sentences.english: Wagon-flow allocation is indispensable contents in the stage plan in a marshalling station.
sentences.chinese: 配流是编组站阶段计划不可缺少的内容。

sentences.english: It is preferred that the different boxes, bulkheads etc be grouped together.
sentences.chinese: 建议一起编组使用不同的接线盒和隔板等。

sentences.english: The students were regrouped according to height and weight.
sentences.chinese: 学生们按身高和体重重新进行了编组。

sentences.english: The indispensability and principle of the automatic classification humping yard system is introduced in this paper.
sentences.chinese: 本文介绍了编组驼峰自动化系统的必要性和工作原理。

sentences.english: Using the prediction model, it predicts wagon's transfer time of the Xiangtangxi Marshalling Station.
sentences.chinese: 利用该模型，对向塘西编组站中时进行了预测。
